ActForeign Missions and International Organizations Act
SubjectUnited Nations University International Network on Water, Environment and Health — Privileges and Immunities Order
PrecisUNITED NATIONS UNIVERSITY INTERNATIONAL NETWORK ON WATER, ENVIRONMENT AND HEALTH PRIVILEGES AND IMMUNITIES ORDER (UNU-INWEH) in order to grant (1) legal status to the United Nations University (UNU) the International Network on Water, Environment and Health (INWEH); and (2) UNU-INWEH officials, personnel, and experts on mission privileges and immunities under the Headquarters Agreement.
